Tesseract (.NET wrapper for the Tesseract OCR engine)

- Path: vendor/Tesseract/
- Author: Charles Weld and Tesseract .NET wrapper contributors
- License: Apache License 2.0 (Apache-2.0)
- Source: https://github.com/charlesw/tesseract
- License file: vendor/Tesseract/LICENSE.txt
- Note: This is the managed .NET wrapper. Yagu's OCR worker uses it as an
  alternative OCR engine (notably on x86/arm64, where the PaddleOCR native
  runtime is unavailable). The full Apache 2.0 license text is retained at
  vendor/Tesseract/LICENSE.txt and is available from:
  https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Tesseract and Leptonica native binaries bundled through the Tesseract wrapper

- Paths:
  - vendor/Tesseract/src/Tesseract/x64/tesseract50.dll
  - vendor/Tesseract/src/Tesseract/x86/tesseract50.dll
