  - vendor/Tesseract/src/Tesseract/x86/leptonica-1.82.0.dll
- Tesseract OCR engine: Copyright (C) the Tesseract contributors, licensed under
  the Apache License 2.0. Source: https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract
- Leptonica image-processing library: Copyright (C) Dan S. Bloomberg and
  Leptonica contributors, licensed under the Leptonica license (a BSD 2-Clause
  style license). Source: https://github.com/DanBloomberg/leptonica

